tailwindcss-types

tailwindcss-types

Installation

npm install --save tailwindcss-types

npm install --save-dev tailwindcss-types

Summary

This package containsalltype definitions fortailwindcss(https://tailwindcss.com).

Links

Refer toTypedoc-https://git-init-wesley.github.io/tailwindcss-types/docs

RequestIssue-https://github.com/git-init-wesley/tailwindcss-types/issues
